[MPR121 Module]        [Arduino Uno]
----------------        --------------
VCC  ---------------->  3.3V
GND  ---------------->  GND
SDA  ---------------->  A4
SCL  ---------------->  A5
ADD  ---------------->  GND  (for default I2C address)
IRQ  ----[optional]

T0–T11  → Connect foil, wire, or conductive material (as touch inputs)

[Speaker/Buzzer]
+     ----------------> D9
-     ----------------> GND
